{"word":"G69 - ἀγρυπνέω - agrypnéō - ag-roop-neh'-o - Watch","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀγρυπνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">agrypnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ag-roop-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Watch</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழித்திரு"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Ultimately from <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5258 - ὕπνος - hýpnos - hoop'-nos/5258\">G5258</a>; to <i>be sleepless</i>, that is, <i>keep awake:</i> - watch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}